    <h2> IFRS 16 “Leases” implementation </h2>
    <p> The adoption of IFRS 16 “Leases” will have a profound impact on some business changing significantly the face of their profit or loss and balance sheet alongside key performance indicators and how executives are remunerated. </p>
    <br>
    <p> Our IFRS 16 implementation guidance will come in the form of a report covering the following areas: </p>
    <ul>
      <li> An outline of the transition options available to you and practical expedients which can be applied. </li>
      <li> Where lease information is available an assessment of the impact each option will have on your financial statements, both on date of adoption and forecast impact for future financial reporting periods. </li>
      <li> Impact of adoption of IFRS 16 on other areas of the annual reporting process including impairment. </li>
      <li> Recommendations of new processes which need to be implemented as a result of adopting IFRS 16.   </li>
